    <p>{`Accessibility is everyone’s responsibility, and the purpose of this document is to provide general accessibility guidelines to developers and designers.`}</p>
    <p>{`{:toc}`}</p>
    <h2>{`Overview`}</h2>
    <p>{`Our products should be accessible to all. At minimum, features should comply to the requirements listed in `}<a parentName="p" {...{
