    <p>{`Making our products accessible benefits everyone, not just people with disabilities. Below are some examples of use cases in which accessibility is important:`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">
        <p parentName="li"><strong parentName="p">{`Visual`}</strong>{`: blindness, low vision, color blindness, using a screen reader or related assistive tech for lifestyle reasons (e.g. long car commute), machine readability and screen scraping technologies`}</p>
