    <h3>{`Visual accessibility`}</h3>
    <p>{`Be mindful when using small font size, thin font weight, low contrast colors in designs as it can severely affect usability.`}</p>
    <p>{`Instead of relying solely on color to communicate information, always combine color with another factor, like shape or position change. This is important because some colors can be hard to tell apart due to color blindness or weak eyesight.`}</p>
