    <p>{`We do client side scanning of inaccessible elements in development environment. The inaccessible elements will be styled with red borders with an onclick alert and console warnings.`}</p>
    <h3>{`External tools`}</h3>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">
        <p parentName="li">{`Google Chrome provides an `}<a parentName="p" {...{
